description._content: Collection: NASA Johnson Space Center Collection Title: Gemini 9 configured extravehicular spacesuit assembly Description: Test subject Fred Spross, Crew Systems Division, wears the Gemini 9 configured extravehicular spacesuit assembly. The legs are covered with Chromel R, which is a cloth woven from stainless steel fibers, used to protect the astronaut and suit from the hot exhaust thrust of the Astronaut Maneuvering Unit.
